(755, 140, 'right_content', '<h3>“FACE YOUR DREAMS.</h3>\r\n<h4>Beauty leads to a natural confidence which gives us courage\r\nto put our heart and soul into achieving our deepest desires\r\nand our most yearned for dreams.”</h4>\r\nEvie – brings out the best in every woman – without changing who they are. Born\r\nfrom the unique, personal experiences of Natalie Wong – chief inspiration officer of\r\nEvie, accidental entrepreneur, passionate motivator, unwavering optimist,\r\npersistent perfectionist, super-mom and more. For a decade, Natalie Wong enjoyed\r\nthe fruits of a fulfilling career in the corporate world of investment banking. Her\r\nendless ambitions, although rewarding – eventually took a toll on her flawless skin.\r\nUnsatisfied with the products on the market, no matter how luxurious they\r\nappeared to be, she concocted her own skincare line – first in her kitchen, and later\r\nin a leading laboratory. Armed with her innate instincts, creative and strategic\r\ntalents, and colored by her international experience – her dream of enhancing\r\nbeauty in every woman was realized. Always believing in driving true results – she\r\nwas able to fulfill a simple premise – beauty always has a purpose.'),
